Included are is the package for deciding the step length satisfying the 
strong Wolfe conditions. It includes the following files:

linesearch.m
bracketing.m
sectioning.m
interpolation.m
fun.m
grad.m

In order to use this package, one has to modify the subroutines fun.m and 
grad.m, and the calls of them in bracketing.m and sectioning.m.

This package was written by: 

Zhaosong Lu
Simon Fraser Univeristy
Canada

October 23, 2008

